            is a tool used to gather statistics about
<application>gstreamer</application> operations
          </para>
          <indexterm zone="gstreamer10 gst-stats-1.0">
            <primary sortas="b-gst-stats-1.0">gst-stats-1.0</primary>
          </indexterm>
        </listitem>
